<HEADLINE>
<P>
DESERT BILL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * As you know, we were finally able to enact the California Desert Protection 
Act in the final hours of 103rd Congress (Oct. 9). 
</P>
<P>
 Our success after a long and difficult road was due in no small part to the 
consistent editorial support voiced by The Times. We made sure your editorials 
were given wide circulation here on Capitol Hill and they helped convince a 
majority of members to approve this far-reaching legislation. Your editorial of 
Oct. 7 was particularly helpful. 
</P>
<P>
 The Times should feel proud of its role in winning protection for this unique 
and beautiful area. 
</P>
<P>
 REP. GEORGE MILLER, Chairman 
