(1-5) 28-31, K.C. San Diego 2. Houston (1-5) 8-11, Cleveland Philadelphia 3. 
New Orleans (2-5) 22-36, S.D. L.A. Rams 4. Washington (1-6) 16-19, Buddy Indy 
5. Grampa Bay (2-4) Idle S.F. 6. Raiders (2-4) 17-20, Miami (Fla.) Atlanta * 
</P>
