 **Also known as Refrigerator. 
</P>
<P>
 A new definition of the two-way player? NBC's Dick Enberg referred to one 
hard-rushing Raider defensive lineman this way Sunday: "Jerry Ball is unable to 
stop the penetration of Jerry Ball." 
</P>
<P>
 Fans will be arguing over this one for years: New Orleans Coach Jim Mora said, 
"A year ago . . . I was standing up there before them at 5-2. This year, I was 
standing up before the team at 2-5. This year's team would beat last year's 
team." 
</P>
