 Kennedy d. Granada Hills, 15-8, 15-5, 15-4 -- Kelly Samuel had eight kills and 
Kristian Ongoco had seven aces to lead Kennedy (4-5, 3-3) in a Northwest Valley 
Conference match. 
</P>
