 Newbury Park d. Westlake, 15-6, 15-5, 15-3 -- Julie Wastell had seven kills 
and four aces and teammate Kari Norberg added 19 assists and seven digs for 
host Newbury Park in the Marmonte League match. 
</P>
<P>
 The victory kept Newbury Park (10-2, 8-2) in a tie for second in the league 
with Thousand Oaks. 
</P>
