 Alemany d. Harvard-Westlake, 15-12, 15-6, 3-15, 15-7 -- The Indians surprised 
the Wolverines (8-4, 5-1), who had previously lost only one game in league 
play. Kelly McKay had 14 kills and Jolene Small 12 and five blocks as Alemany 
(6-4, 4-2) recorded the upset in the "Airdome," the school's temporary 
gymnasium. 
</P>
