recorded 18 kills as L.A. Lutheran (9-2, 6-1) rallied to hand Viewpoint (9-2, 
7-1) its first loss in Heritage League play. 
</P>
<P>
 Canyon d. Burroughs, 15-10, 12-15, 15-11, 15-10 -- Suzy Babko had 12 kills and 
Christy Russell 10 in a losing cause for the Indians (9-3, 4-2 in Foothill 
League play). 
</P>
<P>
 L.A. Baptist d. Western Christian, 15-2, 15-9, 15-10 -- Darcy Frazier recorded 
