2.0 Hits Magazine Tip of the Week 
</P>
<P>
 The highly anticipated music video channel being jointly launched by Warner 
Music, Sony, PolyGram, EMI and BMG appears to be on the back burner amid 
questions if it will ever become a reality. Insiders say recently enacted cable 
legislation has made the venture more costly than originally projected, while a 
