 * 
</P>
<P>
 A. Keith Plant has been appointed to the new position of vice president for 
new business development at Western Digital Corp. in Irvine. Plant, who joined 
the computer products company in 1988, was most recently vice president and 
general manager of the Paradise and TakeCharge products business. 
</P>
