<TEXT>
<P>
 Four cheese products produced by a Wilmington company were ordered recalled 
from store shelves after a harmful bacteria was discovered in a cheese sample, 
state officials reported Thursday. 
</P>
<P>
 No illnesses were linked to the tainted cheese. 
</P>
<P>
