<TEXT>
<P>
 Al Mijares, superintendent of the Bakersfield City School District, is being 
courted by the Santa Ana Unified School District for its top job. 
</P>
<P>
 Mijares recently was interviewed by the Santa Ana school board, said schools 
spokeswoman Diane Thomas.The board is seeking a replacement for Rudy M. 
Castruita, who left in July to head the San Diego County Department of 
