 A Bakersfield school district trustee said he believes Mijares is Santa Ana's 
top pick, according to a report in the Bakersfield Californian. 
</P>
<P>
 Thomas declined comment on Mijares' ranking. 
</P>
<P>
 Mijares, 41, took over the Bakersfield superintendency in January, 1993. He 
could not be reached for comment. 
