recent biography? Comedy writer Tony Peyser reports she now refers to him only 
as "the son formerly known as Prince." 
</P>
<P>
 The once future king won't say whether he'll seek a divorce, says Mills: "But 
he does say he's a great admirer of King Henry VIII." 
