<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102194-0314 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 090876 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 21, 1994, Friday, Valley Edition 
</P>
